.opencode/skills/sk-doc/assets/flowcharts/approval_workflow_loops.md:7:## 1. OVERVIEW
.opencode/skills/sk-doc/SKILL.md:28:- Workflow: [readme_creation.md](./references/readme_creation.md) | Template: [readme_template.md](./assets/readme/readme_template.md)
