.opencode/skills/deep-improvement/references/skill-benchmark/scenario_authoring.md:21:Each scenario is a public/private pair under `assets/skill-benchmark/fixtures/<skill-id>/`. The public half is the only material that crosses the dispatch boundary; the private half is scorer-only gold. Author fixtures in three tiers to manage circularity, publish the T1-T2 score gap as the circularity meter, and aim for one admitted fixture per router key.
