.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/026-memory-database-refinement/review/iterations/iteration-034.md:134:**YAML body not re-parsed:** `parseMemoryContent` at `memory-parser.ts:237-289` extracts frontmatter via `extractFrontmatterBlock` and separately strips it for body extraction. The body content after stripping is never re-parsed as YAML — it is used as plain text. This is correct and intentional.
