.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/z_archive/022-hybrid-rag-fusion/009-perfect-session-capturing/016-json-mode-hybrid-enrichment/001-initial-enrichment/scratch/agent-output-iter-001-A3.md:20:In `input-normalizer.ts`, when the AI provides explicit `triggerPhrases`, they are copied to `_manualTriggerPhrases` (line 451). These manual phrases are then passed to `buildSessionSummaryObservation()` as `facts` (line 278-279, line 550). However, the downstream template/frontmatter rendering likely adds auto-extracted phrases ON TOP of the manual ones, creating a diluted set where the intentional domain-specific phrases are buried among noise.
