.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/026-graph-and-context-optimization/002-spec-kit-internals/002-skill-advisor/changelog/changelog-008-012-skill-advisor-setup-command.md:81:- Parent spec folder still fails strict TEMPLATE_SOURCE check. The parent 006-skill-advisor/ has 4 files (spec.md, plan.md, tasks.md, implementation-summary.md) with template_source_hint: past line 20 of frontmatter, invisible to the validator's head -n 20 sample. Same systemic bug as this child had before fixing. Out of scope for this packet; would require a repo-wide frontmatter normalization pass.
